    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6493874/" class="title-link">篇幅适中的民国史入门书籍</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6493874"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/76720605/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u76720605-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/76720605/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">阿布</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-01-05"
      class="main-meta">2014-01-05 13:42:26</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6493874_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  学术性比剑桥中华民国史高，内容比较客观，篇幅也适中，适合入门者。当然要说完全都好那也不是，但总体算是相当不错了。  学习民国史以此本为主剑桥为辅，看完后可以入门了。如果要找最详细的，那就只好去翻中华书局的那套了。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6493874/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
